    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚最大的酿酒商因美国关税而受益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/australia-s-top-winemaker-reports-soft-demand-for-cheap-bottles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官蒂姆·福特 (Tim Ford) 表示，包括 Treasury Wine Estates Ltd. 在内的澳大利亚酿酒商将受益于中美贸易战，这可能导致其他原产国对葡萄酒的需求下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/australia-s-top-winemaker-reports-soft-demand-for-cheap-bottles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元和贸易成为焦点，黄金价格再度上涨，逼近纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/gold-xauusd-holds-near-2-900-as-traders-weigh-trade-fears-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元和美国国债收益率下跌，黄金价格上涨，并逼近历史最高水平，交易员评估美国为结束乌克兰战争所做的努力，以及唐纳德·特朗普总统在贸易方面的破坏性举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/gold-xauusd-holds-near-2-900-as-traders-weigh-trade-fears-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 00:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚铁矿石枢纽准备迎接 2007 年以来最强飓风</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/zelia-strengthens-into-severe-cyclone-on-track-for-australia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚铁矿石枢纽正面临至少 2007 年以来最强飓风的袭击，威胁到港口设施以及力拓集团和必和必拓集团等公司运营的大型矿山。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/zelia-strengthens-into-severe-cyclone-on-track-for-australia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:53:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普放弃与俄罗斯谈判结束乌克兰战争 油价进一步下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与美国总统弗拉基米尔·普京同意就结束乌克兰战争进行会谈，引发市场猜测俄罗斯供应风险可能缓解，随后油价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美俄会谈推动股市上涨、欧元走强：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美俄会谈激发乌克兰战争结束的预期，亚洲股市上涨。中国市场前景改善也提振了风险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡零售交易员避开国内股票，转向热门的美国股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/singapore-retail-traders-shun-stocks-at-home-for-buzzy-us-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔文·陈 (Kelvin Tan) 于 2018 年开始进行网上投资，和许多新加坡人一样，他把所有的钱都投入了本地股票。两年后，他完全转向了美国股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/singapore-retail-traders-shun-stocks-at-home-for-buzzy-us-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:51:39 GMT</pubDate>
